 <learningAssessmentbody>
  <lcInteraction>
   <lcMultipleSelect id="evaluating">
    <lcQuestion>When evaluating your need for custom plugins, what should you consider? (Choose all
     that apply)</lcQuestion>
    <lcAnswerOptionGroup>
     <lcAnswerOption>
      <lcAnswerContent>What types of output you need.</lcAnswerContent>
      <lcCorrectResponse/>
     </lcAnswerOption>
     <lcAnswerOption>
      <lcAnswerContent>How much your output requirements differ from the DITA OT’s default
       outputs.</lcAnswerContent>
      <lcCorrectResponse/>
     </lcAnswerOption>
     <lcAnswerOption>
      <lcAnswerContent>The way your output should look.</lcAnswerContent>
      <lcCorrectResponse/>
     </lcAnswerOption>
     <lcAnswerOption>
      <lcAnswerContent>How the structure of your source content affects the DITA OT’s publishing
       capabilities.</lcAnswerContent>
      <lcCorrectResponse/>
     </lcAnswerOption>
    </lcAnswerOptionGroup>
    <lcFeedbackIncorrect>When evaluating your need for custom plugins, you should consider what
     types of output you need, how much your output requirements differ from the DITA OT’s default
     outputs, the way your output should look, and how the structure of your source content affects
     the DITA OT’s publishing capabilities.</lcFeedbackIncorrect>
   </lcMultipleSelect>
  </lcInteraction>
 </learningAssessmentbody>
